86
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:12,340
and you've been helping me search for the booklet all along.

87
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,920
So, both emotionally and rationally,

88
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,870
I had to save you.

89
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:18,330
Thank you, Lord.

90
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,420
Don't thank me yet.

91
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:26,330
I actually have one more favor to ask.

92
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,270
City Lord, you flatter me.

93
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:32,450
I'm just a little thief.

94
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:35,150
What could I possibly help you with?

95
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,039
Help me stop someone from...

96
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,120
starting a rebellion.

97
00:08:44,410 --> 00:08:45,270
Yu Xiaolin?

98
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,040
I've been frail and sickly since childhood.

99
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:53,040
My younger brother is healthy

100
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:54,260
and talented,

101
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,960
so he was more favored by our father.

102
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:59,320
So, the entire city thought

103
