106
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,340
must have seen Yu Xiaolin's cruelty and viciousness,

107
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,590
which is why he didn't pass on the position

108
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,150
of the city lord to him.

109
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:21,270
That's right.

110
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:24,510
But my younger brother doesn't think so.

111
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:28,220
My father left behind a treasure

112
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,510
and split the map into three parts.

113
00:09:32,490 --> 00:09:33,570
When my brother found out,

114
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,760
he started searching for them.

115
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,510
If he truly finds them,

116
00:09:39,660 --> 00:09:40,970
