119
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:51,510
why you asked the Shenyin Sect to go to any lengths

120
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,910
to stop Yu Xiaolin from getting the booklet.

121
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,200
So now,

122
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,440
I need you to do the same thing for me.

123
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,000
Master Xie,

124
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:06,390
